Identification of self-antigen-specific T cells reflecting loss of tolerance in 
autoimmune disease underpins preventative immunotherapeutic strategies in 
rheumatoid arthritis.

Law SC(1), Benham H(2), Reid HH(3), Rossjohn J(4), Thomas R(5).

Author information:
